OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be partly cloudy with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, heavy at first. Then the rest
OL,8,Fof the night will see variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud and some showery rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FVariable cloud and bright
OL,12,Fspells in the morning with a
OL,13,Fscattering of showers, these mainly in
OL,14,Fthe south. Becoming dry with
OL,15,Fincreasingly bright or sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping through the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
